description:
Contents:
 - Snow White Boa Coat "Fashionable warm coat with a fuzzy woolen lining."
 - Kid's Snow White Boa Coat "Fashionable, warm kid's coat with a fuzzy woolen lining."
 *You can buy it at any time in the game shop( Clothing Store in Castle St. ) when you purchase it.
 - Snow White Fur Beret "A warm beret made from the fur of beasts."
 *You can buy it at any time in the game shop( Fashion Store in Castle St. ) when you purchase it.
name: Snow White Boa Coat Set
